name: ActiveMQ Classic
description: ActiveMQ Classic is the tried and trusted open-source message broker from Apache ActiveMQ. It supports industry standard protocols like AMQP, STOMP, and MQTT as well as many advanced features while fully supporting JMS 1.1 and J2EE 1.4. It is released under the Apache 2.0 License.
